{"tid":1437992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰塑新形象「MOVE BEYOND」開啟新一章","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:41:30.000Z","uid":217441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4dc81367439e492756b29d1a49923c1b70a11f1","tid":1437992,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】之前神神秘秘話噚日有神秘活動嘅國泰（0293），原來係要同大家宣布公司推出新口號「志在飛躍（MOVE BEYOND）」。行政總裁何杲話，現時<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">航空業界</span></strong></span>競爭環境有唔少改變，亦有唔少新機會，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認為國泰係時候開啟新一章</span></span></strong>，所以藉住全新口號去重塑企業品牌形象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新一章係咩意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：諗唔通，無野講"},{"pid":"124edf39bf69e5212f422ef2027ba67545989b67","tid":1437992,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"POST錯台"},{"pid":"b90ee2fb1412421d33c6afa0d627b5698137994a","tid":1437992,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"究竟咩係新一章"},{"pid":"35ca95580c0d185e945b65030e3f0276b31671a3","tid":1437992,"uid":13125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"今次跪左，就咩形象都唔洗要"},{"pid":"968895f1e1cfadd461656e3436732c48c5d223c8","tid":1437992,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"正式比國航全資收購"}]}